{"tid":1263185,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"本港樓價指數連升5個月並再","createTime":"2019-06-28T04:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T05:28:12.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ebdd9f0820a50651d1962ea2e3e7dcf6afa359bd","tid":1263185,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T04:55:21.000Z","msg":"本港私人樓售價節節上升。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190628/_2019062810391279708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190628%2F_2019062810391279708.jpg&h=d3cc8a56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港樓價指數連升5個月並再創新高。差餉物業估價署今日公布，5月份私人住宅售價指數報396.8點，按月升1.4%，較去年7月份394.8的歷史高位還要高，但升幅較4月份放緩。總結今年首5個月，樓價指數共升10.4%，較去年同期的8%升幅還多。<br />\n<br />\n面積430平方呎以下的細單位樓價創新高，按月升0.8%，較去年8月份的高位多0.7%。今年以來，細單位樓價已升逾10%。面積1000平方呎以上的大型單位樓價也破頂，按月升2%。<br />\n<br />\n就上車盤方面，港島區的平均售價為766萬，升逾2%；九龍區均價647萬，升近1%；新界區均價592萬，升1%。<br />\n<br />\n5月份租金指數報194.9點，按月升約0.36%。總結今年首5個月共升0.83%，遠低於去年同期的2.2%升幅。"},{"pid":"cc8734a7c3495e9520cbf66656c60656e34db496","tid":1263185,"uid":169697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"同期CCL 只係升左9.9%<br />\n原來柒頭的花生講都好啱<br />\nCCL一啲都唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n花生仔仲唔出黎拎彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}